{"word":"G2040 - ἐργάτης - ergátēs - er-gat'-ace - Labourer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐργάτης</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ergátēs"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>er-gat'-ace"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Labourer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வேலையாள், ஊழியக்காரன் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a workman, a laborer, a worker, perpetrator"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G2041 - ἔργον - érgon - er'-gon/2041\">G2041</a>; a <i>toiler</i>; figuratively a <i>teacher:</i> - labourer, worker (-men)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1753 - ἐνέργεια - enérgeia - en-erg'-i-ah/1753\">G1753</a>, <a href=\"#/G1754 - ἐνεργέω - energéō - en-erg-eh'-o/1754\">G1754</a>, <a href=\"#/G1755 - ἐνέργημα - enérgēma - en-erg'-ay-mah/1755\">G1755</a>, <a href=\"#/G1756 - ἐνεργής - energḗs - en-er-gace'/1756\">G1756</a>, <a href=\"#/G2038 - ἐργάζομαι - ergázomai - er-gad'-zom-ahee/2038\">G2038</a>, <a href=\"#/G2039 - ἐργασία - ergasía - er-gas-ee'-ah/2039\">G2039</a>, <a href=\"#/G2040 - ἐργάτης - ergátēs - er-gat'-ace/2040\">G2040</a>, <a href=\"#/G2041 - ἔργον - érgon - er'-gon/2041\">G2041</a>, <a href=\"#/G2108 - εὐεργεσία - euergesía - yoo-erg-es-ee'-ah/2108\">G2108</a>, <a href=\"#/G2109 - εὐεργετέω - euergetéō - yoo-erg-et-eh'-o/2109\">G2109</a>, <a href=\"#/G2110 - εὐεργέτης - euergétēs - yoo-erg-et'-ace/2110\">G2110</a>"}]}